item.title: This years camp is coming soon. We will start Friday evening June 10th and run through Monday late afternoon June 13th, 2016. We are very excited about this year and hope you can join us for more fun and hopefully a lot more sun. Please go to www.greatlakescamp.org and click on the red button to register.
